NOW that you have:

A VALID ARTIFACT REGISTRY REPOSITORY: custom-ai-execution-repository
A SUCCESSFULLY BUILT and PUSHED DOCKER IMAGE: gcr.io/ai-execution-system/custom-ai-execution:latest in your Artifact Registry!

Here's a HIGH-LEVEL OUTLINE of the NEXT PHASE - VERTEX AI DEPLOYMENT:

Navigate to VERTEX AI in Google Cloud Console: We will use the Google Cloud Console (GUI) for the initial deployment setup as it provides a visual and guided approach for Vertex AI Custom Container deployments.
Create a CUSTOM CONTAINER DEPLOYMENT on VERTEX AI Endpoints: We will define a Vertex AI Endpoint and deploy your Docker container image to it.
Specify CONTAINER IMAGE PATH: We will tell Vertex AI where to find your Docker image in Artifact Registry (gcr.io/ai-execution-system/custom-ai-execution:latest).
Configure MACHINE RESOURCES & SCALING: We will define the compute resources (CPU, memory, GPU if needed) for your deployment and configure scaling options.
Set up HEALTH CHECKS (Optional but Recommended): We can configure health checks to ensure Vertex AI monitors the health of your deployed container.
DEPLOY and TEST! We will deploy the endpoint and then TEST your deployed AI Execution System by sending it requests and verifying it is working as expected in the Vertex AI environment!
LET'S START with the VERY FIRST STEP of the VERTEX AI DEPLOYMENT process!

ACTION 1.6.28: NAVIGATE to VERTEX AI in GOOGLE CLOUD CONSOLE

Please follow these steps to navigate to the Vertex AI section in your Google Cloud Console:

OPEN your WEB BROWSER and go to the GOOGLE CLOUD CONSOLE: https://console.cloud.google.com/

ENSURE you are in the CORRECT GOOGLE CLOUD PROJECT: Make absolutely sure that the PROJECT NAME displayed at the top of the Google Cloud Console is ai-execution-system (your project ID). If it's not, switch to the ai-execution-system project using the project selector dropdown at the top.

NAVIGATE to VERTEX AI:

In the LEFT-HAND NAVIGATION MENU of the Google Cloud Console, SCROLL DOWN until you find the "ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE" section.
Under "ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE," CLICK on "Vertex AI."
This will take you to the main Vertex AI dashboard page in the Google Cloud Console.
Once you are on the VERTEX AI DASHBOARD page, REPORT BACK "VERTEX AI DASHBOARD REACHED!"
